from vendor\nSkills Highlights Entry invoices to system (tax input)\nEntry salary adjustment for closing activity\nLeadeship Receiving and checking internal reimbursement\nGood teamwork skill Approval routing for vendor invoices, checking staff\nComplex problem solver journals\nResponsibility Create SOP for Reimbursement and Account Payable\nOptimistic\nProcedures\nLike to learn the new things\nReconcile Prepaid and Accrue Expense\nLanguanges PT Gunung Sewu Kencana Oct 2014 - May 2017\nHolding Company - South Jakarta\nEnglish\nAcct. , Finance, & Tax Staff\nBahasa\nPrepare Financial Statements for around 20companies\n(12 active, 8 no activity) and report to acct. manager\nOrganizational\nReconcile bank statement every month, recon GL\nAccount for prepaid expense, recon interest income from\nSenat, Trisakti School of deposito, recon Tax Art 21 with data from payroll, SPT\nManagement - 2011 to 2012 Masa Tax Art 21 and GL\n(Member of Science Div.) Maintain Fixed Assets (reconcile depreciation between\nVolley, Tarakanita Vocational of SAP Program and recap manual database, maintain FA\nHigh School - 2009 to 2011 (Head of number, stocktake)\nOrganization) Prepare tax invoice, invoice, & AP Voucher\nAcolyte, Kristus Salvator Church - Update data Vendor SAP\n2009 to 2011 (Head of Organization) Entry journal voucher and adjustment journal, closing\nAcolyte, Kristus Salvator Church - around 20 companies (subsidiary companies) within\n2008 to 2009 (Cordinator of Public 4days calender\nRelation) Prepare data for external auditor\nOSIS, Regina Pacis Junior High Recap and reconcile/equalization Tax Art 23/26, 4 (2), and\nSchool - 2005 to 2006 (Member of VAT with GL.\nPublic Relation) Prepare tax for payment and report everymonth Tax Art\n23/26, 4 (2), 25, and VAT also SPT Badan every year, with\nEducation e‐SPT & eFaktur\nRecap and reconcile Prepaid Tax Art 23, also collecting\nfrom Bussiness Units.\n2010 - 2014\nConsolidated FS (using template)\nTrisakti School of Management\nRe